node.text:
If you truly want to be great, spend every waking hour helping others to be great first.🔥🤔💯😏

So many people want to be Kings and Queens yet they do not know how to be Servants. And they will fail because they desire power but not responsibility. Even worse, they want power for themselves and not for the good of others. This attitude is not only arrogant but will surely lead to destruction.

node.text:
♟♟♟I did my best to fight back the tears, but eventually my tears won and I broke down. 

Until you have had to borrow money till your next payday. 
Until you had to hide your car so it doesn't get repossessed, 
Until you had to rush home from work to take the late notice off your door so your neighbors won't see it.

Until you have had to BEG the finance department not to disconnect your cell phone so you can get a phone call for a job. 
Until you have had to borrow gas money to get home from WORK. 
Until you have had to take side jobs to make ends meet. 
Until you have had to go to work WITHOUT lunch money. 
Until you have had to sell everything to get ahead. 
Don't tell me it's HARD, you just don't want it bad enough.

People have asked me why do I share my story and my response is simple: "You have no idea the journey I have been on.  The many sleepless nights.  The many times I have wanted to give up.  The number of "no's" I have been told.  The number of doors that have been shut." 

I share my story of being a struggling immigrant in hopes that I inspire other immigrants, women, men and juveniles that life is NOT over after incarceration or probation or any mishap or mistake. 

I went from being evicted to now the famous “Coach Legend”, Entrepreneur, Motivational Speaker, and soon to be Author. 

If you are tired of being counted out.  Need some direction and clarity in your life.  Then let me HELP you achieve those goals.  Book a strategy session with me TODAY:

node.text:
10 THINGS TO KNOW IF YOU WANT TO DOMINATE IN BUSINESS AND IN LIFE👇🏼
.
1. The man on top of the mountain didn’t just fall there. Pay your dues!
.
2. Most people overestimate what they can achieve in one year and underestimate what they can achieve in five years.
.
3. Leadership is always the problem, leadership is always the solution.
.
4. The thoughts that occupy your mind and the people that you surround yourself with are the two biggest determining factors to your success... or failure.
.
5. Your body is a direct reflection of what’s taking place in your mind.
.
6. The greatest sense of significance you will have is when you’re in service to others. 
.
7. In life you’ve got two chances at a parent/child relationship. Ones when you were the child, and one again when you are the parent - don’t mess it up!
.
8. Not everyone should be an entrepreneur, and that’s okay. You might be happier and find more fulfillment being an INTREprenuer and working for someone you respect in an industry that you love.
.
9. The pain of regret is always worse than the pain of effort.
.
10. 6’s and 7’s cannot lead 8’s and 9’s. If you want to lead good people, start by leading YOURSELF to greatness first!
.
Happy Sunday Everyone 💎🔨

node.text:
💯💯💯 I’ve started businesses when I didn’t have the money 💰. 

I’ve paid for mentors and courses when I didn’t have the money 💴. 

I’ve went to Seminars when I didn’t have the money 💵. 

I’ve invested in myself and bought tools, books, and other resources when I didn’t have the money 💰. 

So that’s why today - I don’t have a job anymore but I still got money 💰. 

Most people wait until they get their stuff together to get their stuff together but if you never get your stuff together when your stuff is not together then your stuff will never be together ❗️

If you truly want to be great, spend every waking hour helping others to be great first.🔥🤔💯😏

So many people want to be Kings and Queens yet they do not know how to be Servants. And they will fail because they desire power but not responsibility. Even worse, they want power for themselves and not for the good of others. This attitude is not only arrogant but will surely lead to destruction.

In today’s world, attention is becoming rarer by the day. 

But if you can take hold of peoples' attention... 

You can change their lives. 

And if you can change their lives, you'll make a great income.

That's why I’ve invested a lot of time into Youtube and other social media platforms. 

Because that’s where the eyeballs are. 

If you’re building a personal brand or a business, which social media platform are you taking advantage of? 

Share with me in the comments.

node.text:
Who do you take advice from?
.
Your parents?... Society?... Your friends?...
.
I know they might have the best intentions for you to become successful, however, does their advice lead to the life you want to live?
.
Remember, if you follow their advice, you take their life.
.
Now that you know this, whose advice are you going to follow to achieve your goals? Comment below.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Coach Legend in DREAM BIG. May be an image of 2 people, bedroom and text.

node.text:
When I didn't have any money, I still had the perception that I would achieve success overnight, literally overnight! 

Now that I have achieved financial freedom, I have realized there is no easy or fast way to success. Success comes after years of preparation in personal and educational growth…the secret is to work hard and Never Give Up!!

Be focused ~ Put 100% of yourself into your goals
Believe in yourself and fight for your dreams
Be persistent
Rely on your strengths
Maintain your momentum and go to the next level.

Go to the top and be the winner
Maintain your passion in whatever you do 
Risk are vital; do not get comfortable 
Success is a group effort; however, leadership is following one voice
Never give up!
